-MiBuU13EaKmGOMjJF-X.description: While there isn't a baby growing yet, your partner's body is getting ready for pregnancy.

-LiBuU13EaKmGOMjJF-Y.description: The tiny life inside your partner (which is technically an embryo) is implanting in the uterus, where it will grow and develop.

-BiBuU13EaKmGOMjJF-Z.description: The bulk of the baby's development is already complete, but your little one more than puts these final weeks before birth to good use.

-PiBuU13EaKmGOMjJF-A.description: You've reached the milestone everyone's been counting down to from the beginning
